	<header class="header wrapper">
		<div class="header__iconCell">
			<i class="fas fa-balance-scale"></i>
			<h1 class="h1">申訴處理表</h1>
		</div>
		<br>
		<div class="header__textCell">
			<div class="rich-text">
				<p style="line-height:0; margin-bottom:5px;"><span class="--mb--rich-text" data-boldtype="0" style="font-weight:400; font-size:28px; color:rgb(16, 16, 16); font-style:normal; letter-spacing:0px; line-height:28px; text-decoration:none;">申訴目的</span></p><p style="line-height:0; margin-bottom:5px;"><span class="--mb--rich-text" data-boldtype="0" style="font-weight:400; font-size:28px; color:rgb(16, 16, 16); font-style:normal; letter-spacing:0px; line-height:28px; text-decoration:none;">為增進團結和諧、保障員工權益，協助員工解決工作上有關個人權益或不公平待遇等事項。</span></p><p style="line-height:0; margin-bottom:5px;"><span class="--mb--rich-text" data-boldtype="0" style="font-weight:400; font-size:28px; color:rgb(16, 16, 16); font-style:normal; letter-spacing:0px; line-height:28px; text-decoration:none;">一般申訴範圍</span></p><p style="line-height:0; margin-bottom:5px;"><span class="--mb--rich-text" data-boldtype="0" style="font-weight:400; font-size:28px; color:rgb(16, 16, 16); font-style:normal; letter-spacing:0px; line-height:28px; text-decoration:none;">員工於在職期間發生下列情事，並能證明者，得提出申訴：</span></p><p style="line-height:0; margin-bottom:5px;"><span class="--mb--rich-text" data-boldtype="0" style="font-weight:400; font-size:28px; color:rgb(16, 16, 16); font-style:normal; letter-spacing:0px; line-height:28px; text-decoration:none;">一、因現行之制度、規章、辦法或行政措施未盡事宜或執行疏失，致損</span><span class="--mb--rich-text" data-boldtype="0" style="font-weight:400; font-size:28px; color:rgb(16, 16, 16); font-style:normal; letter-spacing:0px; line-height:28px; text-decoration:none;">害其合法權益者。</span></p><p style="line-height:0; margin-bottom:5px;"><span class="--mb--rich-text" data-boldtype="0" style="font-weight:400; font-size:28px; color:rgb(16, 16, 16); font-style:normal; letter-spacing:0px; line-height:28px; text-decoration:none;">二、對獎懲之決定有異議，且有具體證明者。</span></p><p style="line-height:0; margin-bottom:5px;"><span class="--mb--rich-text" data-boldtype="0" style="font-weight:400; font-size:28px; color:rgb(16, 16, 16); font-style:normal; letter-spacing:0px; line-height:28px; text-decoration:none;">三、因其他員工之違法、濫權或不當對待行為，致侵犯權益或影響</span><span class="--mb--rich-text" data-boldtype="0" style="font-weight:400; font-size:28px; color:rgb(16, 16, 16); font-style:normal; letter-spacing:0px; line-height:28px; text-decoration:none;">正常工作者。</span></p><p style="line-height:0; margin-bottom:5px;"><span class="--mb--rich-text" data-boldtype="0" style="font-weight:400; font-size:28px; color:rgb(16, 16, 16); font-style:normal; letter-spacing:0px; line-height:28px; text-decoration:none;">四、對職務升遷、或工作調派認為處置不當，而影響其權益者。</span></p><p style="line-height:0; margin-bottom:5px;"><span class="--mb--rich-text" data-boldtype="0" style="font-weight:400; font-size:28px; color:rgb(16, 16, 16); font-style:normal; letter-spacing:0px; line-height:28px; text-decoration:none;">五、其他與公務有關，有提申訴之必要且能證明者。</span></p><p style="line-height:0; margin-bottom:5px;"><span class="--mb--rich-text" data-boldtype="0" style="font-weight:400; font-size:28px; color:rgb(16, 16, 16); font-style:normal; letter-spacing:0px; line-height:28px; text-decoration:none;"><br></span></p>
